Flask Web Application with AWS Elastic Beanstalk & RDS (MySQL)
📌 Project Overview

This project demonstrates deploying a Python Flask web application on AWS Elastic Beanstalk and integrating it with an Amazon RDS MySQL database. It showcases a real-world cloud architecture where a web application interacts with a managed database securely.

