☁️ Deployment Steps
1. Initialize Beanstalk
eb init
2. Create environment
eb create myapp-env
3. Set environment variables
eb setenv DB_HOST=<RDS-ENDPOINT> DB_USER=admin DB_PASS=<PASSWORD> DB_NAME=<DB_NAME>
4. Deploy
eb deploy
